Posts.Content: Aug 22, 2006 05:33AM LImomof3 wrote: Hi Patty. Sorry you got that phone call. According to my onc, Neulasta is supposed to last 14 days. Good luck and I hope your counts come back up quickly. It was great to hear that you were feeling good thought. It gives all the rest of us hope. Maria
